  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_5_15391-15525",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "15391-15525",
      "markText": "温德米尔夫人　是不是所有的男人都坏？ 柏维克公爵夫人　哦，都坏，亲爱的，个个都坏，无一例外。而且他们永远不会变得好些。男人会变老，但决不会变好。",
      "totalCount": 896,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=15391&rangeEnd=15525",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=15391&rangeEnd=15525"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_5_3710-3756",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3710-3756",
      "markText": "当一个男人向一个女人有口无心地说上一大堆空话的时候，为什么他自以为一定能使对方喜欢得不得了？",
      "totalCount": 630,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3710&rangeEnd=3756",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3710&rangeEnd=3756"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_7_16537-16591",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "16537-16591",
      "markText": "这个世界上只有两种悲剧。一种是得不到你所要的；另一种是得到你所要的。后一种要糟糕得多；后一种才是真正的悲剧！",
      "totalCount": 615,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=16537&rangeEnd=16591",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=16537&rangeEnd=16591"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_6_14918-14961",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "14918-14961",
      "markText": "男人与女人之间不可能有什么友谊。有的只是热恋、仇恨、倾慕、爱情，但不是友谊。我爱您——",
      "totalCount": 594,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14918&rangeEnd=14961",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14918&rangeEnd=14961"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_7_17501-17530",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "17501-17530",
      "markText": "玩世不恭的人知道每一件东西的价格，却不知道任何东西的价值。",
      "totalCount": 414,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=17501&rangeEnd=17530",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=17501&rangeEnd=17530"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_7_7552-7622",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "7552-7622",
      "markText": "但是，即便他有一千个外遇，您也必须留在你们的孩子身边。即便他对您粗声大气，您也必须留在您的孩子身边。即便他虐待您，您也必须留在您的孩子身边。",
      "totalCount": 405,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7552&rangeEnd=7622",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7552&rangeEnd=7622"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_6_7329-7396",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7329-7396",
      "markText": "如今丈夫当众表示尊重妻子是十分危险的。人们照例会这样想：这个丈夫私下里一定在打老婆。世人对于任何看起来像美满姻缘的现象怀有极大的戒心。",
      "totalCount": 391,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7329&rangeEnd=7396",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7329&rangeEnd=7396"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_5_22723-22825",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "22723-22825",
      "markText": "温德米尔勋爵　正经的女人可真够顽固的！ 温德米尔夫人　不正经的男人可真够脆弱的！",
      "totalCount": 385,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=22723&rangeEnd=22825",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=22723&rangeEnd=22825"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_6_16581-16717",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "16581-16717",
      "markText": "达林顿勋爵　这必须当机立断：要么现在；要么拉倒。 温德米尔夫人　（从沙发上站起来）那么就拉倒！",
      "totalCount": 374,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16581&rangeEnd=16717",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16581&rangeEnd=16717"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_7_16692-16711",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "16692-16711",
      "markText": "一个不爱我的女人？哦，我能爱她一辈子！",
      "totalCount": 374,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=16692&rangeEnd=16711",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=16692&rangeEnd=16711"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_6_11554-11577",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "11554-11577",
      "markText": "她像一本法国黄色小说专门销往英国市场的豪华版。",
      "totalCount": 363,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=11554&rangeEnd=11577",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=11554&rangeEnd=11577"
    },
    {
