    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_5_16753-16787",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "16753-16787",
      "markText": "哭鼻子是丑女人寻找慰藉的手段，但是漂亮的女人哭鼻子就意味着彻底失败。",
      "totalCount": 323,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=16753&rangeEnd=16787",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=16753&rangeEnd=16787"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_5_7057-7079",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7057-7079",
      "markText": "因为做丈夫的道德败坏，做妻子的就得学他的样？",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7057&rangeEnd=7079",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7057&rangeEnd=7079"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_7_14849-14936",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "14849-14936",
      "markText": "这是女人最坏的地方。她们总是要你变好归正。可要是她们遇见我们的时候我们本来就很规矩，她们压根儿不会爱上我们。她们喜欢发现我们坏得不可救药，又喜欢把规矩得毫无吸引力的我们撇下。",
      "totalCount": 299,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14849&rangeEnd=14936",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14849&rangeEnd=14936"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_8_12143-12217",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "12143-12217",
      "markText": "昨晚我的一个幻觉破灭了。我原以为我身上已经没有心。其实我有，而一颗心对我是不合适的，温德米尔。不知怎么的，它和摩登的时装总不相称。它会使人老态毕露。",
      "totalCount": 273,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=12143&rangeEnd=12217",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=12143&rangeEnd=12217"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_5_7311-7374",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7311-7374",
      "markText": "好人在这个世界上造成的危害很大。当然，最大的危害在于他们对待坏事过于认真。其实，划分好人和坏人是荒唐的。人要么可爱，要么可厌。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102923&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7311&rangeEnd=7374",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cc32780813ab8eb4g01319a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7311&rangeEnd=7374"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102923_6_15781-15858",
      "chapterUid": 6,
